Decentralized Reputation Network L1
Overview

Decentralized Reputation Network L1 enables verifiable reputation scores across multiple Web3 platforms and communities.

Features

Portable reputation identity

Trust scoring algorithms

Sybil-resistant verification

Multi-platform reputation tracking

On-chain verification logs

Architecture
Identity Layer

Manages decentralized identities.

Reputation Engine

Calculates reputation scores.

Data Aggregation Module

Collects interaction data.

Verification Layer

Ensures authenticity of reputation signals.

Use Cases

DAO contributor reputation

Freelance marketplaces

Web3 community governance

Trust-based marketplaces
